Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.58,0:22:03.82,Yuri004-ED-JP-land-2,,0,0,10,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}明日も　ずっと
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.82,0:22:06.54,Yuri004-ED-JP-land-2,,0,0,10,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}続きますように
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.54,0:22:12.76,Yuri004-ED-JP-land-2,,0,0,10,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}願い込めた空
