Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.56,0:22:19.48,Yuri004-ED-JP-side-2,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}聞こえるから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.48,0:22:22.35,Yuri004-ED-JP-side-2,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}この歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.35,0:22:25.11,Yuri004-ED-JP-side-2,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}響かせよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.11,0:22:27.28,Yuri004-ED-JP-side-2,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}どんな時でも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.28,0:22:29.49,Yuri004-ED-JP-side-2,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}二人で　乘り越えてゆ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.49,0:22:34.26,Yuri004-ED-JP-side-2,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}こう譲れない絆を
