Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.35,0:22:25.11,Yuri004-ED-CHS-side-2,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}于我心中回响
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.11,0:22:27.28,Yuri004-ED-CHS-side-2,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}无论何时啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.28,0:22:29.49,Yuri004-ED-CHS-side-2,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}两人一起　乘风破浪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.49,0:22:34.26,Yuri004-ED-CHS-side-2,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}这份坚不可摧的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.26,0:22:41.37,Yuri004-ED-CHS-side-2,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}独一无二不可替代　是因为你呀
